content: Kinda of boring, but I paid two dollars so I'm stuck with it.    When I play,  there is a "mutiplier" in the corner, but there is no where that I have found that tells you what or where this "mulitplier" is for or how it can help you in the matching of this game.   Any suggestions, anyone?
replyContent: Thank you very much for playing the Istrys. The score multiplier goes up if you make a new match within 2.5 seconds of a previous match. Since you are giving 10 x current multiplier points per match you can get a much higher final score with a chain of matches which raise your multiplier. Thank you again for playing.
